## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the inherent biases present in the sources. Additionally, while the report provides a broad overview, it may not capture all nuances of how stereotypes are perpetuated across different media platforms and cultural contexts. Further research could explore the impact of digital media and social networks on the perpetuation of stereotypes.

